txtReportParameters: Folder: Field Ops SHS - Inbox, Filter:  Incident ID STARTS WITH , Sort:  Incident Ascending

column9: RequestDescription
Equipment - Scouter: Scouter device won't turn on. Has been dropped multiple times during training.
Equipment - Gravity Room: Gravity chamber is stuck at 500x Earth normal gravity. Teacher cannot adjust settings.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Laptop screen keeps flickering. Started after the energy blast training session.
Equipment - Scouter: Scouter battery is dead. Need replacement battery pack for power level readings.
Equipment - Time Chamber: Door lock is jammed. Students cannot exit the hyperbolic time chamber after training.
Equipment - Scouter: Display screen on scouter is cracked. Power levels cannot be read accurately.
Communication Equipment: Capsule vehicle radio is not transmitting. Cannot contact training teams in the field.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Desktop computer keeps overheating. Air conditioning unit is not keeping up with equipment demands.
Equipment - Gravity Room: Emergency exit button is unresponsive. Safety concern for trainers inside.
Networking Equipment: Internet connection drops every hour. Wi-Fi extender may be failing.
Equipment - Energy Meter: Energy detection device is showing false readings. Calibration needed.
Equipment - Scouter: Multiple units not syncing with central database. Cannot update power level readings.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Monitor is displaying in monochrome. Color settings reset unexpectedly.
Equipment - Scouter: Audio feedback speaker is blown out. Silent mode only on all units.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Install/Move: Printer will not communicate with network. Cannot print training schedules.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Desktop tower making loud grinding noise. Hard drive may be failing.
Equipment - Scouter: Device keeps resetting to factory settings. Memory card may be corrupted.
Networking Equipment: VPN connection failing for remote training sessions. Cannot access central server.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Laptop randomly shuts down during long training simulations.
Equipment - Gravity Room: Power supply is unstable. Gravity levels fluctuate between 100x and 1000x Earth normal.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Install/Move: Scanner not recognizing documents. Calibration needed for power level charts.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Printer paper jam error won't clear. Sensor may need replacement.
Equipment - Scouter: Unit is overheating after 30 minutes of use. Cooling fan damaged.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: USB ports on desktop not recognizing flash drives. Driver issue suspected.
Computer, printer, scanner, etc. -- Repair: Mouse cursor jumps around randomly. Input device unresponsive.
Equipment - Time Chamber: Air filtration system making squealing noise. May need maintenance.
